Damn I was looking up leaked images in Minase Seri's twitter just to find out that he did not make an anal scene for this anthology smh, I'm DISAPPOINTED, anyways I was kinda expecting something more ambitious from this but turns out I just got the typical standard OH anthology doujin just like the others, though I admit this anthology had quite the highlights an example would be Ayato Ayari's segment where he finally set the bar high when it comes to his art, he has improved A LOT ever since the time he disappeared, I'm very impressed, next highlight would be Binbi for taking it top a notch when it comes to intensity and sex positions my blood pressure actually rose because of how hot it looked, the next would be Inochi Wazuka's part, though I may not be a fan of his art, I gotta admit he puts so much detail into the ass holes.
